  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<blockquote><p>Prerequisite: Level 9+ Warlock, Pact of the Tome invocation</p></blockquote><p>Immediately after a creature casts a spell that targets you or includes you in its area of effect, you can use take a Reaction to make an ability check using your Warlock spellcasting ability. On a success, you steal the knowledge of the spell if it is at least a level 1 spell and of a level you can cast (it can be a spell from any spell list). For the next 8 hours or until you use this feature again, you know the spell and can cast it using your spell slots. The DC equals 10 plus the spell's level.</p>",
